Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:21.98,pm,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1300,228)\c&000000&\3c&HF2F2F2&\fs44\bord15\blur30\b1}战士候补生 {\b0\fs}\N\N由「恶魔」艾尔迪亚人少年少女{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}组成的少年兵部队。{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}他们在马莱军的监视下接受严酷的训练，{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}通过成绩、品行、技术、人格、{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}为国献身的意志等考核项目进行选拔。{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}只有艾尔迪亚人能继承{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}九大巨人，因此必须有身为「恶魔」{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}却担负国防重任的艾尔迪亚人存在。{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}被选为战士的艾尔迪亚人{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}及其父母和子女将获得{\fs27}\N\N{\fs}「名誉马莱人」的身份。
Comment: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.02,op-cn,,0,0,0,,=====OP=====
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:04:00.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走出黑暗 重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:03.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直至光芒 照亮结局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑恶嘴脸 咒骂不止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.27,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:16.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:23.75,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童绞尽脑汁 只为保护手中硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:30.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:37.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童手中 紧攥最后一枚硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.22,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毁灭与重生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.07,op-en,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:04:00.06,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's start a new life from the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:03.14,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Until the light reveals the end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.94,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sinister faces, growing curses
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.27,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my last war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:16.99,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels playing disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:23.75,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:30.25,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:37.26,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.22,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.47,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
